This New Zealand-based centre is one of the pioneering institutions for inquiry into the emergence and development for models of relational and non-authoritarian spirituality.

John Heron is the author of the book [[Sacred Science]], developed a 'Cooperative Inquiry' model of human and spiritual research, and the site is rich with texts and resources on the topic.

